<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Pass Fast Driving School</title>

<style>
body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  background: #fff;
  color: #111;
}

header {
  background: #000;
  color: #fff;
  padding: 15px;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
}

header h1 {
  font-size: 20px;
}

.btn {
  background: #FFD700;
  color: #000;
  padding: 10px 15px;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: bold;
  border-radius: 5px;
}

.hero {
  padding: 60px 20px;
  text-align: center;
}

.hero h2 {
  font-size: 32px;
}

.hero p {
  font-size: 18px;
  margin: 20px 0;
}

.cta-buttons a {
  margin: 10px;
  display: inline-block;
}

.section {
  padding: 40px 20px;
  text-align: center;
}

.pricing {
  background: #f5f5f5;
}

.card {
  margin: 20px auto;
  padding: 20px;
  max-width: 300px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  background: white;
  box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

footer {
  background: #000;
  color: #fff;
  padding: 20px;
  text-align: center;
}

.sticky-call {
  position: fixed;
  bottom: 10px;
  left: 10px;
  right: 10px;
  background: #FFD700;
  padding: 15px;
  text-align: center;
  font-weight: bold;
  border-radius: 8px;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
  <h1>Pass Fast Driving</h1>
  <a href="tel:07123456789" class="btn">Call Now</a>
</header>

<section class="hero">
  <h2>Pass Your Driving Test FAST 🚗</h2>
  <p>Book your first lesson within 24 hours</p>

  <div class="cta-buttons">
    <a href="tel:07123456789" class="btn">Call Now</a>
    <a href="#booking" class="btn">Book Online</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
  <p>✔ 80%+ Pass Rate</p>
  <p>✔ Manchester Based Instructors</p>
  <p>✔ Manual & Automatic Lessons</p>
</section>

<section class="section pricing">
  <h2>Pricing</h2>

  <div class="card">
    <h3>Manual</h3>
    <p>£33 / hour</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h3>Automatic</h3>
    <p>£35 / hour</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <h2>Struggling to Pass?</h2>
  <p>We help you gain confidence, get a test fast, and pass first time.</p>
</section>

<section class="section" id="booking">
  <h2>Book Your Lesson</h2>
  <p>Fill in your details and we’ll contact you ASAP.</p>

  <form>
    <input type="text" placeholder="Your Name" required><br><br>
    <input type="tel" placeholder="Phone Number" required><br><br>
    <button class="btn">Submit</button>
  </form>
</section>

<footer>
  <p>© 2026 Pass Fast Driving School</p>
</footer>

<div class="sticky-call">
  📞 Call Now: 07123 456789
</div>

</body>
</html>
